{"tid":2131901,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美澳增巡南海軍艦 聯手抗華","createTime":"2020-07-30T06:35:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T10:02:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"71efd6698545225db33dc45c692891899037b086","tid":2131901,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T06:35:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200730/ZLMIWZ7DO6V4OWUUDYSYMRBACE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200730%2FZLMIWZ7DO6V4OWUUDYSYMRBACE%2F&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhJKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=6586c71e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200730%2FZLMIWZ7DO6V4OWUUDYSYMRBACE%2F&h=aaecdb13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200730/ZLMIWZ7DO6V4OWUUDYSYMRBACE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n美澳增巡南海軍艦 聯手抗華<br />\n<br />\n「天下圍中」局勢越漸明顯，。。。。。。。。。。，未來可能成為「六眼聯盟」。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲外交部部長佩恩（Marise Payne）承諾，澳洲將與聯同美國、英國、新西蘭及加拿大的「五眼聯盟」，以及聯同美國、印度及日本的「四國同盟」加強溝通合作。美澳兩國表明非常關注中國近月的舉動，包括打壓新疆維族人及香港問題。美澳協議主要聚焦軍事及外交層面，兩國將成立工作小組，在印太問題上打擊中國的「大外宣」；亦承諾增加在南海及印度洋巡邏，使之成為常態。兩國亦共同宣佈，中國在南海的主張完全不合乎國際法，但澳洲未表明到南海島礁12海里內航行是「自由航行」。她又稱，澳洲在文明理性的角度評估中國問題，強調「澳洲沒有甚麼意欲去傷害中澳關係」。<br />\n<br />\n美國及澳洲的聯合聲明亦有支持台灣，。。。。。。。。。，各國視台灣為印太區域不可或缺的合作夥伴。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部發言人汪文斌回應指，美。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/cSptQxORhaxicCZ9E-scqozy3yM=/664x442/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KYLMGSOAJJC7EUOB57GTKF3IJA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FcSptQxORhaxicCZ9E-scqozy3yM%3D%2F664x442%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKYLMGSOAJJC7EUOB57GTKF3IJA.gif&h=3cd4b609&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蓬佩奧（右）與澳洲外長佩恩會面，商議對抗中共政策。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日稱有意加入「五眼聯盟」<br />\n<br />\n除了美澳，美日兩國亦有新合作。。。。。。。。。。。他承諾一旦日本受攻擊，美國將提供援助。<br />\n<br />\n路透社／法新社"},{"pid":"0ec0d752514ea3eea29715a7a1d9f0b01577c6d7","tid":2131901,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T06:36:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d52f07a1757f86220354ff1a69443438d9bb7212","tid":2131901,"uid":121672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T06:39:43.000Z","msg":"YEAH!!<br />\n今次唔知會有幾多國聯手打中國呢?<br />\n好期待"},{"pid":"19fc7ec1d40e992da0dcb68d7e294c080d317d3a","tid":2131901,"uid":177168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T09:34:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d516bd9bbc1f9931b367bf69d9d4ac16cb56216b","tid":2131901,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T09:42:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n八國聯軍再現"},{"pid":"d5f3094a73bec0b38edebe6232ad5918a94c6ac1","tid":2131901,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T09:44:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"844a2372b8d63e5f67f267a3a53c5b652606e552","tid":2131901,"uid":61653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T09:44:52.000Z","msg":"中國共產黨=現代恐怖主義組織"},{"pid":"84abcfdeafb2b2d570874ceedd7f0cc2ccad6130","tid":2131901,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T09:45:24.000Z","msg":"八國聯軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb8aa274324e81f87b361256bd1fe24d97a0045b","tid":2131901,"uid":66546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T09:47:08.000Z","msg":"百國聯軍<br />\n<br />\n中國真係抵撚死"},{"pid":"ce9c45e9dd72751edc382ece9ebafd38771f8272","tid":2131901,"uid":210682,"